{"tid":2490995,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日政府推Q版「氚寶」被罵爆 緊急下架滅火","createTime":"2021-04-16T04:11:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T06:18:08.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"43b9f204a0fac533746558a2d293e6e4683d6b49","tid":2490995,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:11:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRqqhFeLQt9nKSSui3Trj1G3MDLD1j4n8dQgoCgvcxGms?filename=pUw4Prz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpUw4Prz.jpg&h=39c43359&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVpmxu2zieg3NsxUTLh8PyuDEAUmtRCnehvo7Y2mX7SqB?filename=nH6gFyf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnH6gFyf.jpg&h=aead97bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmbx49ABEVjKGQB4QXiwvT7JRHsLFYBKvUg39FkGUBKV1Y?filename=0hkUsdg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0hkUsdg.jpg&h=3c6e07ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本政府正式決議將福島核一廠核含氚核廢水排入太平洋，震驚全世界。為了向日本民眾<br />\n宣導，日本復興廳將放射性物質「氚」擬人化，變成類似吉祥物的可愛娃娃，並製作宣傳<br />\n文宣、短片。想不到此舉引起日本民眾不滿，復興廳不敵民怨，只好將問世短短1天的「<br />\n氚寶」下架。<br />\n <br />\n日本政府13日確定將福島核廢水稀釋排放入海，東電會使用先進的液體處理系統處理核廢<br />\n水，但仍然無法去除放射性物質「氚」（tri），日本計劃將氚濃度稀釋至每公升少於<br />\n1,500貝克 （becquerels，衡量放射性活躍度國際單位），此濃度是日本安全標準允許的<br />\n1/40，世衛可飲用水標準的1/7。放流計劃最快2022年開始，預計將耗時30年。<br />\n <br />\n為使民眾更加了解「氚」，復興廳同日發布宣傳文宣和短片，綠色的「氚寶」頭上有原子<br />\n結構，它會存在於雨水、海洋中，人們可以喝下含氚的自來水，氚會隨著水分排出體外，<br />\n並不會在殘留在體內。<br />\n <br />\nQ版「氚寶」頭上有原子結構。（翻攝東京新聞網站）<br />\n <br />\n文宣清楚顯示「氚寶」會存在於雲雨、海洋、自來水中，並會隨著水分排出體外。（翻攝<br />\ncosumo_pori_tan推特）<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n復興廳是2011年3月11日東日本大震災後，日本政府以災後重建為目的，所設置的中央行<br />\n政單位。復興廳負責人表示，擬人化的「氚」並不是要做吉祥物，而是為了更平易近人，<br />\n讓民眾更加理解核廢水的安全性及科學根據，並沒有善惡區分。不過日本民眾不買帳，在<br />\n網路砲轟政府有問題，有繪師甚至畫了「氚寶同人圖」，只是同人版氚寶面色猙獰恐怖，<br />\n像是會吃人的怪物。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n日本繪師繪製「氚寶同人圖」，形象恐怖猙獰。（翻攝matuda推特）<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n事隔1天，復興廳於14日撤下相關文宣，表示：「對於13日公布的文宣和影片，我們收到<br />\n了國民各式各樣的聲音與感想，在此基礎上，我們決定修改放射性氚的設計形象，因此暫<br />\n時撤下宣傳海報及影片。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/OXaGlD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2FOXaGlD&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwJa0YVntLK4LebkCjpCDSOM%3D&h=a92d640c\" target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/OXaGlD</a>"},{"pid":"04f6cf1e708e2748b9030b4ef8360cbb59c2ab4e","tid":2490995,"uid":52215,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />架佬真係仆街含家剷"},{"pid":"7ff8f2d0296de747e2a40e0535f50d2483eb2c1e","tid":2490995,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:45:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ed2c8e24b73a7b897ab52db831f8b3fcdcf870e","tid":2490995,"uid":26385,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:46:34.000Z","msg":"火水救火<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cd2173467bb1e43677a4be4c4f2127699734157","tid":2490995,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:48:57.000Z","msg":"好奇等d水蒸發唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38349b52ec2dc2fe2a845db9b9da700084b308e0","tid":2490995,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:51:05.000Z","msg":"on9 pr<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3eaa50d64e93f461b89e7b784c47aa2f39d13ba","tid":2490995,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:51:52.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a22128cb02e50e016da8f03c1f1ba8ac80f9078","tid":2490995,"uid":59922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:53:36.000Z","msg":"唔提就等丟淡，走去整隻嘢出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class